packageJson.name: fastify-website
packageJson.description: A static website builder for Fastify using metalsmith

scripts.build:website:watch: npm run build:website && chokidar 'src/website' -c 'npm run build:website'
scripts.build: npm run build:cleanup && npm run build:create-temp-folder && npm run build:get-releases && npm run build:process-releases && npm run build:website
scripts.test: npm run test:lint && npm run test:images
scripts.start: npm run build && npm run start:server

packageJson.author: Luciano Mammino

repoDetails.name: website
repoDetails.description: This project is used to build the website for fastify web framework and publish it online.

packageJson.name: point-of-view
packageJson.description: Template plugin for Fastify

scripts.test: standard && tap -J test/* && tsc

packageJson.author: Tomas Della Vedova - @delvedor (http://delved.org)
